  </section>

  <section id="starting_working">
    <title>Proofreading in <app>PoProofRead</app></title>
    <p>To do a proofreading with the program follow these steps:</p>
    <steps>
      <item><p>Open the podiff you wish to proofread
      e.g. <file>example.podiff</file></p></item>
      <item><p>Move though the document with the navigation buttons or
      the <link xref="user_shortcuts">keyboard shortcuts</link></p></item>
      <item><p>When you encounter a diff part that you would like to
      comment on then simply start typing your comment</p></item>
      <item><p>If it is a large diff part and you wish to make
      comments in the middle of the diff part (in-line comments) then
      activate the in-line mode (with the control or the <link
      xref="user_shortcuts">keyboard shortcut</link>)</p></item>
      <item><p>When you are done with the proofreading, save your
      work, and the formatted output will be available in the file
      <file>example.podiff.ppr.out</file>. This will contain only the
      diff parts you commented on and your comments.</p></item>
    </steps>

  </section>
